sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant TAS as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as PVC / Database
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant LMESCtrl as LMEval Controller
    participant LMEvalPod as LMEval Pod<br/>+ Driver Sidecar
    participant OrchRoute as Orchestrator Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OrchKRBP as Orchestrator kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8432/TCP HTTPS
    participant Orchestrator as Orchestrator Container<br/>8032/TCP HTTP
    participant Detectors as Detector InferenceServices<br/>HTTPS TLS
    participant TargetIS as Target InferenceService<br/>HTTPS TLS
    participant EHRoute as EvalHub Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Providers as Provider Pods<br/>(Garak, GuideLLM, etc.)

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: TrustyAI Model Explainability
    Client->>Route: HTTPS/443<br/>Route-level auth
    Route->>KRBP: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (serving cert)
    KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview
    KRBP->>TAS: HTTP/8080<br/>localhost (no TLS)
    TAS->>Storage: PVC read/write or<br/>JDBC (optional TLS)
    Storage-->>TAS: Data response
    TAS-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over K8sAPI,LMEvalPod: Flow 2: LMEval Job Execution
    Client->>K8sAPI: POST LMEvalJob CR<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer token
    K8sAPI-->>LMESCtrl: Watch notification
    LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pod<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI-->>LMEvalPod: Pod scheduled
    Note over LMEvalPod: Driver sidecar manages<br/>job lifecycle via exec

    Note over Client,TargetIS: Flow 3: Guardrails Orchestrator Inference Protection
    Client->>OrchRoute: HTTPS/443<br/>Reencrypt TLS
    OrchRoute->>OrchKRBP: HTTPS/8432<br/>TLS (serving cert)
    OrchKRBP->>OrchKRBP: SubjectAccessReview
    OrchKRBP->>Orchestrator: HTTP/8032<br/>localhost
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: HTTPS<br/>TLS, service certs
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator->>TargetIS: HTTPS<br/>TLS, service certs
    TargetIS-->>Orchestrator: Inference response
    Orchestrator-->>OrchKRBP: Combined response
    OrchKRBP-->>OrchRoute: HTTPS response
    OrchRoute-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,Providers: Flow 4: EvalHub Evaluation Orchestration
    Client->>EHRoute: HTTPS/443<br/>Reencrypt TLS
    EHRoute->>EvalHub: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (serving cert)
    EvalHub->>EvalHub: Internal SAR check
    EvalHub->>Providers: HTTPS<br/>TLS, ServiceAccount
    Providers-->>EvalHub: Evaluation results
    EvalHub-->>EHRoute: Response
    EHRoute-->>Client: JSON Response
